sentences: In 2003 she won the solo/duo category at the International Blues Challenge in Memphis, Tennessee.
Boyes' debut US release Lucky 13 was nominated by the Blues Foundation in Memphis, Tennessee for the 2007 Blues Music Awards, 'Contemporary Blues Album of the Year'.
